{"tid":1032633,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股神損手】卡夫亨氏暴挫20% 巴菲特帳面蝕218億","createTime":"2019-02-22T13:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T00:08:52.000Z","uid":32938,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e19d171efa194cd5bfc4142d3b196cdceaf3aca9","tid":1032633,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"卡夫亨氏（Kraft Heinz）上季業績令市場失望，又大幅削減派息，加上被美國證監（SEC）調查公司的會計操作，股價市後跌20%，令「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）旗下投資旗艦巴郡（Berkshire Hathaway）帳面蒸發28億美元（約218億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n卡夫（Kraft）與亨氏（Heinz）兩間公司2015年合併，由巴郡及私募基金3G Capital聯手進行。<br />\n<br />\n根據SEC的文件，巴郡上季持有卡夫亨氏26.7%的股份，市值達155.6億美元（約1,214億港元）。若今季未有變動，巴郡帳面虧損28億美元。<br />\n<br />\n卡夫亨氏是今年第2單巴菲特錄得帳面蒸發的新聞。早前，蘋果（Apple）發盈警，令巴郡一度帳面蒸發27.7億美元（約216億港元），現時Apple股價已收復失地。"},{"pid":"9fad5f4933c93d5f56d7f417e552efee0e7cf376","tid":1032633,"uid":215905,"like":35,"dislike":6,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"個老野out啦 睇佢重貨apple就知"},{"pid":"55f283aa127d09b0e5c95527a05c1ee3681c0a64","tid":1032633,"uid":106426,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1f986986a17c7a707d3535eb2a4e8631ce30388","tid":1032633,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76bf0b522a2779aacff8f3f8f393ef50f8b8a546","tid":1032633,"uid":122318,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsAwtaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsAwtaN.png&h=e6b7a293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4ede06aa68016ed45456bb8eccc2808947c88dd","tid":1032633,"uid":25727,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"早前，蘋果（Apple）發盈警，令巴郡一度帳面蒸發27.7億美元（約216億港元），現時Apple股價已收復失地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm